Class Description
actionCard
The actionCard class serves as an UNO "card" of TYPE: ACTION.
AI
The AI class serves as artificial intelligence player of the game.

AIPanel
The AIPanel shows the all the AIs that the player requested to play against.

The buttonListener class contains the games button listener.
card
The card class is serves as the base card class and is used to create a UNO card object.

The cardDealer class serves dealer of the game.

The cardDeck class serves as the actual deck of cards for the UNO game.

The cardInterface interface represents the properties of each card.

The cardListener class contains the games card listener.
Direction
This class points the direction of where the reverse needs to go.
gameConstants
The gameConstants interface represents the unique constants of each UNO card.
gameController
The gameController class serves as the main control of the game.
gameControlTest  
gameFrame
The gameFrame class represents the main frame of the game its panels to be set up and displayed.
gameSession
The gameSession class controls a session of the game created.
numCard
The numCard class serves as an UNO "card" of TYPE: NUMBER.
Player
The player class will represent each player of the game including AI, and keep track of the player's name and hand which is represented in an array.
playerPanel
The playerPanel class represents each players game panel on the game screen.
rulesDialog
The rulesDialog class represents the rules to be displayed for players on the welcome screen and in the game menu bar.
RunUNO  
tablePanel
The tablePanel class represents the center table of each game to hold cards discarded.
unoConstants
The unoConstants represents the specifics of each card type.
unoGame
The unoGame class serves as an instance of the game.
unoGameTests  
updatePanel
The updatePanel represents the panel of game updates.
welcomeDialog
The welcomeDialog class represents the game set up to be displayed for players on the welcome screen to select from.
wildCard
The wildCard class serves as an UNO "card" of TYPE: WILD.
